ation:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">binom.pmf(num heads, num trials, prob of heads)&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0.0pt;margin-bottom:0.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:'Google Sans';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">binom.pmf(7,10, 0.5) ===&gt; prob of 7 heads&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><br /><br /><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0.0pt;margin-bottom:0.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:'Google Sans';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">binom.cdf(7,10, 0.5) ===&gt; prob of 7 or fewer heads&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><br /><br />","labels":[{"name":"Math"}]}